column5: Nice going Aaron I see the Trigger X drop dead minnow works good.
My bad you used the probe worms from Trigger X.

Wow !!!!! Nothing like the fight of a big bronze tank !!!! Well done Aaron !!! Sounds like you guys got numbers too !!!! The colors of the fish look amazing !!!  Thanks for sharing !!! Tight-lines.  Cheers
awesome day on the water Aaron congrats
Superb day , Aaron and Mitch! Beautiful bronzers for sure. Thanks for sharing.
I have been out there fishing for the last two week got to love Lake Erie bass.Nice fish
I actually saw you guys banging them one after another from shore with my binocks. I can attest to the action. Good going.
WTG Aaron! Those are some Piggies   Sure beats workin'
I like your reports a lot, despite the heavy plugs for products. I guess if u t sponsored it is something u need to do. Landry
Thanks guys. I hope to get out a bit for smallies and muskies the next little while.  Steve, I saw your FB posts with all the smallies while I was still salmon fishing. It was give the smallie itch!
Old Iron maker, I can't hide anywhere eh? LOL Hopefully you can get out there and take advantage of the good fishing soon.
